      "title": "section_4",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Silver_ArmorCC\"><span id=\"Silver_Armor\"></span>Silver Armor<sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Silver\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Silver\">CC</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Silver&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Silver ArmorCC\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Silver Armor is a set of <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Heavy_Armor\" title=\"Skyrim:Heavy Armor\">heavy armor</a> added by the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Silver\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Silver\">Alternative Armors - Silver</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a>. A full set can be recovered through the quest <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:When_the_Cat%27s_Away\" title=\"Skyrim:When the Cat&#39;s Away\">When the Cat's Away</a><sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Silver\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Silver\">CC</a></sup>, while also appearing in random loot starting at level 10. Forging Silver Armor requires the Advanced Armors perk.\n</p><p>Its armor rating surpasses <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Orcish_Armor\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Orcish Armor\">Orcish armor</a> but weighs more, also no shield exists.\n</p><p>The set lacks material keywords, and their absence would normally prevent the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Heavy_Armor#Matching_Set\" title=\"Skyrim:Heavy Armor\">Matching Set</a> perk, however there is a script attached to the set that overrides that behavior and checks to see if the perk should be applied/removed whenever a piece of the set is added or removed.  A similar script is used for <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Daedric#Daedric_Mail_CC\" title=\"Skyrim:Daedric\">Daedric Mail</a> and <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Dwarven#Dwarven_MailCC\" title=\"Skyrim:Dwarven\">Dwarven Mail</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/48/SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg/200px-SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/4/48/SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg/300px-SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/4/48/SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg/400px-SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Silver_Armor_Male.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A male <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Nord\" title=\"Skyrim:Nord\">Nord</a> wearing silver armor</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"3\" class=\"unsortable\">Raw Materials\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\" colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Delta\n</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">Ratio\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Silver_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Silver Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/a3/SR-icon-ingot-Silver_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Silver_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/a/a3/SR-icon-ingot-Silver_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Silver_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/a/a3/SR-icon-ingot-Silver_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Silver_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Silver_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Silver Ingot\">Silver</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-ingot-Iron Ingot.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/24px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/36px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/0/01/SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png/48px-SR-icon-ingot-Iron_Ingot.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Iron_Ingot\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Iron Ingot\">Iron</a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/24px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/36px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/3/3a/SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png/48px-SR-icon-misc-LeatherStrips.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Leather_Strips\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Skyrim:Leather Strips\">Strips</a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Silver_Armor.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"SR-icon-armor-Silver Armor.png\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d2/SR-icon-armor-Silver_Armor.png/48px-SR-icon-armor-Silver_Armor.png\" width=\"48\" height=\"48\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d2/SR-icon-armor-Silver_Armor.png/72px-SR-icon-armor-Silver_Armor.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/d/d2/SR-icon-armor-Silver_Armor.png/96px-SR-icon-armor-Silver_Armor.png 2x\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td><span id=\"Silver_Armor\"></span>Silver Armor<br /><span class=\"idall\">(<span class=\"idref\"><span class=\"idcase\">FE</span><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID#Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\"><span style=\"cursor:help;\" title=\"These three digits vary depending on installed Creations. Click for more details.\">xxx</span></a><span class=\"idcase\">801</span></span>)</span></td>\n<td>40</td>\n<td>400</td>\n<td>42\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\">4</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>3\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black; color:red\">34.7\n</td>\n<td>184\n</td>\n<td style=\"color:red\">7.55\n</td>\n<td>1.85\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-Silv